| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0449 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b2def563-c29e-589a-9e52-c81ccef5e258"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
